articles.title: Australia reports first human case of bird flu in child who contracted it in India - Scroll.in
articles.description: The patient had experienced a severe infection but made a full recovery from the illness, health authorities said.
articles.content:
Australia on Wednesday recorded its first human case of avian influenza, colloquially known as bird flu, in a child who authorities said contracted the infection in India, reported Reuters.
